Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...تذكّرت
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,!يوتا
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,!يوتا -\N!يوتا -
